tourBios.exmtStatus: Conditional - Additional Qualifying Tournament Finisher or Finished 76-100 on 2014 Web.com Tour Money List
tourBios.carHigh: 2014: Finished T112 at Web.com Tour Qualifying Tournament in December...Played two events on the European Challenge Tour...Competed in two events on the Adams Pro Tour and recorded one top-five.
tourBios.otherCarHigh: Voted BIG XII Newcomer of the Year in 2011... Made the BIG XII All-Conference team in 2012... Was a member of the 2012 NCAA National Championship golf team at the University of Texas ...Finished runner-up at the British Amateur in 2013.
tourBios.personal: Would play professional tennis or ice hockey if he weren't playing golf...Would like to trade places with Sidney Crosby for a day and play in an NHL game...Most famous person ever met was Arnold Palmer at a college event at Isleworth CC in Orlando...Enjoys reading books by Bob Rotella...His dream foursome includes Tiger Woods, Jack Nicklaus and Palmer...Favorite motto is "Grip it and Rip it." ...Speaks English, Finnish, Swedish and German...Lists playing Augusta National at the top of his bucket list...Biggest thrill outside golf is playing anything competitive...Twitter handle is @tonihakula.

tourBios.carHigh: 2015: Finished T15 at the Florida Qualifying Tournament, with rounds of 71-68-66-69. Made three cuts with best showing a T60 at The Players Cup in July.
tourBios.personal: Also plays ice hockey and tennis...Hopes to play Augusta National someday...Dream foursome would include Tiger Woods, Arnold Palmer and Jack Nicklaus...Diehard Penguins, Lakers and Broncos fan...Twitter handle is @tonihakula.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T60th in 2015 at the The Players Cup.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T78th in Total Eagles on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA TOUR Canada.
